title: OT124: Opentatonic Thread
summary:
Key ideas:
- This post is an open thread allowing readers to post about any topic they want.
- The DC SSC meetup group is having a party on April 13th and anyone is welcome to attend.
- Claire wants meetup attendees to complete a survey about their experiences.
- An advertisement for the Seattle Anxiety Specialists psychotherapy group is included.

Key learnings:
- Readers can attend the DC SSC meetup party in Washington.
- Anyone who attends meetups can give feedback through a survey.
- The Seattle Anxiety Specialists group helps anxious people in Seattle.

Key questions:
- None provided.
